mendel.serialize

Interface SimpleMap<K,V extends ByteSerializable>


  • public interface SimpleMap<K,V extends ByteSerializable>
    Defines a very basic serializable map that consists of Key, Value pairs wherein the Key can be ascertained by the Value directly. For example, a class that has a 'name' attribute that we wish to use as a lookup key.
    Author:
    malensek
